{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":349,"text":"Living in Africa is to be on the edge,"},{"time":3543,"text":"metaphorically, and quite literally"},{"time":6297,"text":"when you think about connectivity before 2008."},{"time":9929,"text":"Though many human intellectual and technological leaps"},{"time":13641,"text":"had happened in Europe and the rest of the world,"},{"time":16665,"text":"but Africa was sort of cut off."},{"time":19254,"text":"And that changed, first with ships"},{"time":21881,"text":"when we had the Renaissance, the Scientific Revolution"},{"time":25158,"text":"and also the Industrial Revolution."},{"time":27259,"text":"And now we've got the digital revolution."},{"time":30286,"text":"These revolutions have not been evenly distributed"},{"time":33286,"text":"across continents and nations."},{"time":35619,"text":"Never have been."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38349,"text":"Now, this is a map of the undersea fiber optic cables"},{"time":42114,"text":"that connect Africa to the rest of the world."},{"time":45018,"text":"What I find amazing is that Africa"},{"time":47058,"text":"is transcending its geography problem."},{"time":49868,"text":"Africa is connecting to the rest of the world"},{"time":51682,"text":"and within itself."},{"time":53518,"text":"The connectivity situation has improved greatly,"},{"time":56794,"text":"but some barriers remain."},{"time":58995,"text":"It is with this context that Ushahidi came to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62683,"text":"In 2008, one of the problems that we faced"},{"time":67219,"text":"was lack of information flow."},{"time":69757,"text":"There was a media blackout in 2008,"},{"time":72053,"text":"when there was post-election violence in Kenya."},{"time":74429,"text":"It was a very tragic time. It was a very difficult time."},{"time":77253,"text":"So we came together and we created software"},{"time":80003,"text":"called Ushahidi."},{"time":81569,"text":"And Ushahidi means \"testimony\" or \"witness\" in Swahili."},{"time":85169,"text":"I'm very lucky to work with two amazing collaborators."},{"time":88339,"text":"This is David and Erik."},{"time":90445,"text":"I call them brothers from another mother."},{"time":92517,"text":"Clearly I have a German mother somewhere."},{"time":95529,"text":"And we worked together first with building"},{"time":98118,"text":"and growing Ushahidi."},{"time":99566,"text":"And the idea of the software was to gather information"},{"time":102565,"text":"from SMS, email and web, and put a map"},{"time":105338,"text":"so that you could see what was happening where,"},{"time":108253,"text":"and you could visualize that data."},{"time":110357,"text":"And after that initial prototype,"},{"time":112613,"text":"we set out to make free and open-source software"},{"time":115108,"text":"so that others do not have to start from scratch like we did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119959,"text":"All the while, we also wanted to give back"},{"time":121930,"text":"to the local tech community that helped us"},{"time":124162,"text":"grow Ushahidi and supported us in those early days."},{"time":127667,"text":"And that's why we set up the iHub in Nairobi,"},{"time":130250,"text":"an actual physical space"},{"time":132274,"text":"where we could collaborate,"},{"time":134740,"text":"and it is now part of an integral tech ecosystem in Kenya."},{"time":139297,"text":"We did that with the support of different organizations"},{"time":142067,"text":"like the MacArthur Foundation and Omidyar Network."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145072,"text":"And we were able to grow this software footprint,"},{"time":148249,"text":"and a few years later it became"},{"time":151015,"text":"very useful software,"},{"time":153712,"text":"and we were quite humbled when it was used in Haiti"},{"time":156939,"text":"where citizens could indicate where they are"},{"time":160008,"text":"and what their needs were,"},{"time":161402,"text":"and also to deal with the fallout from the nuclear crisis"},{"time":164699,"text":"and the tsunami in Japan."},{"time":166738,"text":"Now, this year the Internet turns 20,"},{"time":170132,"text":"and Ushahidi turned five."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172414,"text":"Ushahidi is not only the software that we made."},{"time":175215,"text":"It is the team, and it's also the community"},{"time":178272,"text":"that uses this technology in ways that we could not foresee."},{"time":182557,"text":"We did not imagine that there would be this many maps"},{"time":185877,"text":"around the world."},{"time":187388,"text":"There are crisis maps, election maps, corruption maps,"},{"time":190910,"text":"and even environmental monitoring crowd maps."},{"time":194437,"text":"We are humbled that this has roots in Kenya"},{"time":197893,"text":"and that it has some use to people around the world"},{"time":200609,"text":"trying to figure out the different issues that they're dealing with."},{"time":203960,"text":"There is more that we're doing to explore this idea"},{"time":206831,"text":"of collective intelligence, that I, as a citizen,"},{"time":209446,"text":"if I share the information with whatever device that I have,"},{"time":212382,"text":"could inform you about what is going on,"},{"time":214925,"text":"and that if you do the same, we can have a bigger picture"},{"time":217783,"text":"of what's going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219627,"text":"I moved back to Kenya in 2011."},{"time":221688,"text":"Erik moved in 2010."},{"time":223836,"text":"Very different reality. I used to live in Chicago"},{"time":225983,"text":"where there was abundant Internet access."},{"time":228133,"text":"I had never had to deal with a blackout."},{"time":230965,"text":"And in Kenya, it's a very different reality,"},{"time":233849,"text":"and one thing that remains despite the leaps in progress"},{"time":236946,"text":"and the digital revolution is the electricity problem."},{"time":240730,"text":"The day-to-day frustrations of dealing with this"},{"time":243501,"text":"can be, let's just say very annoying."},{"time":246737,"text":"Blackouts are not fun."},{"time":248702,"text":"Imagine sitting down to start working, and all of a sudden"},{"time":251615,"text":"the power goes out,"},{"time":253295,"text":"your Internet connection goes down with it,"},{"time":255970,"text":"so you have to figure out, okay, now, where's the modem,"},{"time":259618,"text":"how do I switch back?"},{"time":261607,"text":"And then, guess what? You have to deal with it again."},{"time":264325,"text":"Now, this is the reality of Kenya, where we live now,"},{"time":267517,"text":"and other parts of Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269882,"text":"The other problem that we're facing"},{"time":271838,"text":"is that communication costs are also still a challenge."},{"time":276125,"text":"It costs me five Kenyan shillings,"},{"time":278289,"text":"or .06 USD to call the U.S., Canada or China."},{"time":284342,"text":"Guess how much it costs to call Rwanda, Ghana, Nigeria?"},{"time":288912,"text":"Thirty Kenyan shillings. That's six times the cost"},{"time":292186,"text":"to connect within Africa."},{"time":294296,"text":"And also, when traveling within Africa,"},{"time":296430,"text":"you've got different settings for different mobile providers."},{"time":299696,"text":"This is the reality that we deal with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302405,"text":"So we've got a joke in Ushahidi"},{"time":305020,"text":"where we say, \"If it works in Africa, it'll work anywhere.\""},{"time":309818,"text":"[Most use technology to define the function. We use function to drive the technology.]"},{"time":311970,"text":"What if we could overcome the problem"},{"time":314216,"text":"of unreliable Internet and electricity"},{"time":318081,"text":"and reduce the cost of connection?"},{"time":320106,"text":"Could we leverage the cloud?"},{"time":322072,"text":"We've built a crowd map, we've built Ushahidi."},{"time":323903,"text":"Could we leverage these technologies"},{"time":326328,"text":"to switch smartly whenever you travel from country to country?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":331393,"text":"So we looked at the modem,"},{"time":332691,"text":"an important part of the infrastructure of the Internet,"},{"time":335970,"text":"and asked ourselves why"},{"time":338481,"text":"the modems that we are using right now"},{"time":340436,"text":"are built for a different context, where you've got"},{"time":342660,"text":"ubiquitous internet, you've got ubiquitous electricity,"},{"time":346615,"text":"yet we sit here in Nairobi and we do not have that luxury."},{"time":351652,"text":"We wanted to redesign the modem"},{"time":354149,"text":"for the developing world, for our context,"},{"time":357196,"text":"and for our reality."},{"time":359107,"text":"What if we could have connectivity with less friction?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":362784,"text":"This is the BRCK."},{"time":366313,"text":"It acts as a backup to the Internet"},{"time":369217,"text":"so that, when the power goes out,"},{"time":372994,"text":"it fails over and connects to the nearest GSM network."},{"time":379142,"text":"Mobile connectivity in Africa is pervasive."},{"time":381983,"text":"It's actually everywhere."},{"time":384323,"text":"Most towns at least have a 3G connection."},{"time":387251,"text":"So why don't we leverage that? And that's why we built this."},{"time":390160,"text":"The other reason that we built this"},{"time":392358,"text":"is when electricity goes down, this has eight hours"},{"time":394944,"text":"of battery left, so you can continue working,"},{"time":396958,"text":"you can continue being productive,"},{"time":399046,"text":"and let's just say you are less stressed."},{"time":403268,"text":"And for rural areas, it can be"},{"time":405598,"text":"the primary means of connection."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407701,"text":"The software sensibility at Ushahidi is still at play"},{"time":410437,"text":"when we wondered how can we use the cloud"},{"time":413496,"text":"to be more intelligent so that"},{"time":415438,"text":"you can analyze the different networks,"},{"time":417823,"text":"and whenever you switch on the backup,"},{"time":420962,"text":"you pick on the fastest network,"},{"time":423471,"text":"so we'll have multi-SIM capability"},{"time":425870,"text":"so that you can put multiple SIMs,"},{"time":427966,"text":"and if one network is faster, that's the one you hop on,"},{"time":431380,"text":"and if the up time on that is not very good,"},{"time":434729,"text":"then you hop onto the next one."},{"time":437144,"text":"The idea here is for you to be able to connect anywhere."},{"time":440881,"text":"With load balancing, this can be possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443769,"text":"The other interesting thing for us -- we like sensors --"},{"time":447622,"text":"is this idea that you could have an on-ramp"},{"time":451050,"text":"for the Internet of things."},{"time":452977,"text":"Imagine a weather station that can be attached to this."},{"time":456597,"text":"It's built in a modular way so that you can also attach"},{"time":459336,"text":"a satellite module so that you could have"},{"time":461106,"text":"Internet connectivity even in very remote areas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464631,"text":"Out of adversity can come innovation,"},{"time":467376,"text":"and how can we help the ambitious coders and makers"},{"time":471415,"text":"in Kenya to be resilient in the face of problematic infrastructure?"},{"time":475494,"text":"And for us, we begin with solving the problem"},{"time":477750,"text":"in our own backyard in Kenya."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480694,"text":"It is not without challenge."},{"time":483094,"text":"Our team has basically been mules carrying components"},{"time":485847,"text":"from the U.S. to Kenya. We've had very interesting conversations"},{"time":489041,"text":"with customs border agents."},{"time":490969,"text":"\"What are you carrying?\""},{"time":492767,"text":"And the local financing is not"},{"time":495537,"text":"part of the ecosystem for supporting hardware projects."},{"time":500888,"text":"So we put it on Kickstarter, and I'm happy to say that,"},{"time":503607,"text":"through the support of many people,"},{"time":505848,"text":"not only here but online,"},{"time":507847,"text":"the BRCK has been Kickstarted,"},{"time":510102,"text":"and now the interesting part of bringing this to market begins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":514192,"text":"I will close by saying that, if we solve this"},{"time":517086,"text":"for the local market, it could be impactful"},{"time":519646,"text":"not only for the coders in Nairobi"},{"time":522096,"text":"but also for small business owners"},{"time":524448,"text":"who need reliable connectivity,"},{"time":527112,"text":"and it can reduce the cost of connecting,"},{"time":529312,"text":"and hopefully collaboration within African countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533992,"text":"The idea is that the building blocks of the digital economy"},{"time":538964,"text":"are connectivity and entrepreneurship."},{"time":542483,"text":"The BRCK is our part"},{"time":544923,"text":"to keep Africans connected,"},{"time":547507,"text":"and to help them drive the global digital revolution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551291,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":552505,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}